Package uk.ac.gla.abbi.abbi_library.utilities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Globals
    This class contains constants and global variables that can be used to manipulate the ABBI bracelet's sound emission properties.
    UtilityFunctions
    This class contains utility functions that are used to implement the demo Android application ABBI Remote.
    UUIDConstants
    This class stores the UUID constants (denoting the protocols used by the Android application to connect to and communicate with the ABBI bracelet).
